ZH: 他家里的客厅里有一个精美的佛龛。
EN: There is an exquisite altar in the living room of his house.

ZH: 她每天早上都在佛龛前祷告。
EN: She prays in front of the altar every morning.

ZH: 家中的佛龛上摆放着鲜花和香炉。
EN: There are flowers and incense burners on the altar at home.

ZH: 我们家的佛龛是由纯正的木材制成的。
EN: The altar in our home is made of pure wood.

ZH: 她向佛龛里的佛像行礼。
EN: She pays respect to the Buddha statue in the altar.

ZH: 他在佛龛上放了一个大型的香炉。
EN: He placed a large incense burner on the altar.

ZH: 佛龛里的佛像非常庄严宝贵。
EN: The Buddha statue in the altar is very solemn and precious.

ZH: 我们在佛龛前虔诚地祈祷。
EN: We pray devoutly in front of the altar.

ZH: 这个佛龛是我爷爷从云南带回来的。
EN: This altar was brought back by my grandfather from Yunnan.

ZH: 她经常在佛龛前焚香祈祷。
EN: She often burns incense and prays in front of the altar.

ZH: 佛龛上面挂着一幅祥和的风景画。
EN: There is a peaceful landscape painting hanging above the altar.

ZH: 他的佛龛里摆放着许多信徒送的香炉。
EN: Many incense burners given by believers are placed in his altar.

ZH: 佛龛前摆放着一对光藕香。
EN: A pair of lotus-shaped incense burners are placed in front of the altar.

ZH: 他每天都会在佛龛前给佛像上香。
EN: He burns incense for the Buddha statue in front of the altar every day.

ZH: 小孩子不懂事，把佛龛上的花瓶打碎了。
EN: The child, not knowing any better, accidentally broke the vase on the altar.

ZH: 他决定在新家里设计一个特别的佛龛。
EN: He decided to design a special altar in his new home.

ZH: 佛龛里的香火终年不断。
EN: The incense in the altar burns continuously throughout the year.

ZH: 她手工制作了一个漂亮的佛龛。
EN: She handcrafted a beautiful altar.

ZH: 佛龛里的香火缭绕，散发着沁人心脾的香气。
EN: The incense in the altar curls up, exuding a refreshing fragrance.

ZH: 他在佛龛前默默祈祷。
EN: He silently prays in front of the altar.
